`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Cause_Serious
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'cause serious'  <victim>

 This spell, along with Cause Light, Cause Critical, and Harm, inflicts damage
on the victim through the careful use of applied magical pain energies. The
higher level spells, which of course use more mana, cause more damage to the
victim.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
